{"id": "1361343177759395880", "channel_id": "1361343177759395880", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n 彌薩格大學校務處將於4月14日22:20進行校內設施修復，更新完成後您將得到通知，重新進入遊戲。對於更新可能造成的不便，我們會準備一份補給物資以示歉意。祝大家調查順利！\n\n【補給物資】\n線上維修補償：銀芯*50\n\n【領取條件】\n領取時間截至2025年4月28日23:59。請記得及時前往信箱領取補給物資哦。\n\n【更新内容】\n● 修復「碎裂余夢」存在錯誤的材料來源：「材料置換」的問題。\n● 修復了使用猩紅熔爐時，會觸發使用鑰令相關機制的問題。\n● 修復了「超距」在超維空間中跨戰鬥後，再取出不會降低算力消耗的問題。\n● 修復了成就「聆聽世界的嗡鳴」在未達成條件時偶爾也會觸發的問題。\n● 修復了「怨恨鎖鏈」會錯誤的添加多次封印效果的問題。\n● 修復了事件 「迷夢中的呼喚」在第二章中多次出現的問題。\n● 修復了在部分劇情中選擇選項後，會再次彈出同一選項導致循環的問題。\n● 修復了星辰篇第二章「蛻變」關卡符號顯示錯誤問題。\n● 典藏館更新了星辰篇第一章「重臨霧都」劇情CG。\n● 典藏館更新了星辰篇第二章「蛻變」劇情CG。", "timestamp": "2025-04-14T14:11:46.111000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1361343178174894230", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1361343177759395880/1361343178174894230/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69cc7ee2&is=69cb2d62&hm=5f990ab868bc70f4f7e9647331cad6aadd0c5b79bc3999387a5bbdc883976124&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1361343177759395880", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.0.3 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1361343285074853949", "channel_id": "1361343177759395880", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**V2.2.0.3 Online Maintenance Notice**\n\nDear Keeper,\n    The Mythag University Administration Office will conduct facility repairs on April 14 at 22:20(UTC+8). You will be notified once the update is complete and can re-enter the game. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and will provide a supply package as compensation. Happy investigating!\n    \n【Supply Package】\nMaintenance Compensation: Silver*50\n    \n【Claim Conditions】\nClaim period ends on April 28 2025(UTC+8), at 23:59. Please remember to check your mailbox to claim the supply package.\n     \n【Update Content】\n● Fixed incorrect material source for \"Shattered Dream Remnants\": \"Material Replacement\".\n● Fixed an issue where using the Crimson Furnace would trigger mechanisms related to the use of the Posse.\n● Fixed an issue where \"Transcendence\" would not reduce Arithmetica consumption after being retrieved from Ultra Space post-battle.\n● Fixed an issue where the achievement \"Listening to the World's Buzz\" would occasionally trigger without meeting the conditions.\n● Fixed an issue where \"Resentment Chains\" would incorrectly add multiple sealing effects.\n● Fixed an issue where the event \"Call in the Dream\" would appear multiple times in Chapter 2.\n● Fixed an issue where selecting options in certain storylines would cause the same option to reappear, leading to a loop.\n● Fixed an issue with the symbol display in Chapter 2 of the Starry Saga \"Metamorphosis\".\n● Updated the CG for Chapter 1 \"Return to Mist City\" of the Starry Saga in the Archive.\n● Updated the CG for Chapter 2 \"Metamorphosis\" of the Starry Saga in the Archive.", "timestamp": "2025-04-14T14:12:11.697000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1361343177759395880", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.2.0.3 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
